reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 22, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very inexpensive, reasonably high-capacity thumbdrives
reviews.reviewText: It's amazing how cheap storage has become. They have a great read/write speed, and so far as I can tell, they're of standard construction, and will have good durability. The price is cheap enough to consider them disposable, or lendable (even to less than reliable friends).Color coded, but you can attach a small sticky label for identification, if you'd like.Highly recommended. I just bought a small pocketful.
